{"tid":474071,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［中大工程］大家點睇中大呢科工程","createTime":"2017-11-19T21:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T17:12:39.000Z","uid":33321,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"81af7f03328e27e454bcf356e2ff425516df5cb6","tid":474071,"uid":33321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T21:57:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>System Engineering and Engineering Management (SEEM)</strong><br />\n<br />\nMajor Courses :<br />\nEngineering Economics<br />\nData Structures<br />\nOperations Research I<br />\nOperations Research II<br />\nSystem Simulation<br />\nEngineering Innovation and Entrepreneurship<br />\nComputer Processing System Concepts<br />\nFundamentals in Information Systems<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStreams :(&gt;18 credits)<br />\n1）Business Information Systems<br />\n2）Financial Engineering<br />\n3）Logistics and Supply Chain Management<br />\n4）Service Engineering and Management<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><ins>Business Information Systems</ins></span><br />\nFinancial Markets<br />\nPricing &amp; Revenue Management<br />\nIntroduction to Client/Server Systems<br />\nInformation Systems Analysis &amp; Design<br />\nInformation Systems Management<br />\nHuman-Computer Interaction<br />\nOpen Systems for E-Commerce<br />\nComputational Intelligence for Decision Making<br />\nSystems Design &amp; Implementation<br />\nE-commerce Data Mining<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><ins>Financial Engineering</ins></span><br />\nFinancial Markets<br />\nPricing &amp; Revenue Management<br />\nIntroduction to Client/Server Systems<br />\nFundamentals of Financial Engineering<br />\nComputational Financial<br />\nFinancial Mathematics<br />\nRisk Analysis in Financial Engineering<br />\nInvestment Science<br />\nDifferential Equations<br />\nDynamic Optimization &amp; Applications<br />\nStochastic Models<br />\nDecision Methodology &amp; Applications<br />\nStatistics Modeling and Analysis in Financial Engineering"},{"pid":"a3b084cfa5db1f0ed953ec5c26989067b3cb03df","tid":474071,"uid":33321,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T21:58:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><ins>Logistics and Supply Chain Management</ins></span><br />\nFinancial Markets<br />\nPricing &amp; Revenue Management<br />\nIntroduction to Client/Server Systems<br />\nMarketing Management<br />\nFundamentals of Financial Engineering<br />\nQuality Control and Management<br />\nService Management<br />\nDecision Methodology &amp; Applications<br />\nLogistics Management<br />\nSupply Chain Management<br />\nE-commerce Data Mining<br />\nTechnology, Consulting and Analytics in Practice<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><ins>Service Engineering and Management</ins></span><br />\nFinancial Markets<br />\nPricing &amp; Revenue Management<br />\nIntroduction to Client/Server Systems<br />\nMarketing Management<br />\nQuality Control and Management<br />\nStochastic Model<br />\nService Management<br />\nDecision Methodology &amp; Applications<br />\nSupply Chain Management<br />\nE-commerce Data Mining<br />\nService Systems<br />\nTechnology, Consulting and Analytics in Practice<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEmployment :<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/055324_ce9fb09a01495451e7bdd6a0f1b98787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F055324_ce9fb09a01495451e7bdd6a0f1b98787.jpg&h=16545fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/055416_1b5e27d7e4c2864c5ebbf9576617681e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F055416_1b5e27d7e4c2864c5ebbf9576617681e.jpg&h=bb781e2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df432915aa0def94c57e786c9b0fab6b963c91a7","tid":474071,"uid":33321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply